examples.en: You are such a raving success.
The guy on the corner was raving like a madman.
My friends all think I'm stark raving mad (=completely crazy).
She was no raving beauty, but at least she looked smart.
The old man stood on a street corner, raving at his wife.
My first thought was that I had gone stark raving mad.
Why don't you stop ranting and raving for a minute and listen?
